text:
Thank you for helping me carry the baggage,
Producer.

Sure, no problem.
I'm glad you got to have a fulfilling shopping trip.

On that topic,
Here, take this.

Eh? This is...
Something you bought at that shop right... for me?

Yeah.
I had a good feeling about it, so I went ahead and bought it.

This is... quite unique,
or rather, a pretty wild necktie, isn't it...

Since it's a present from an idol in your charge
Please wear it to our next job site.

To a job...!?
That's a pretty difficult task...

Fufuu
I'm looking forward to it.
